[SN]TITLE[SN]
Boy reported and men charged after Livingston cocaine recovery

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A 15-year-old boy has been reported to the procurator fiscal and two men have been charged after half a kilo of cocaine was recovered in West Lothian.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Police said the Class A drug was found within a commercial property near a school and a house in the Livingston area.
